name: Spring-js
tagline: Javascript agent ideas, tools and love to change the world
body:
### Welcome to Spring-js project in Coronado Land
Spring-js are javascript pieces of software to connect Spring framework from your page. The scripts are ready to use. Just download from [coronadoland/spring-js](https://github.com/coronadoland/spring-js) and use in your code.

### Vision and Mission
I believe that my experience can be shared to help others. This project is my experience wrapped of nice software. 
Using this software you can deploy faster and secure projects and invest your time in other important things.

### License.
The code is free for any project, but read [License agreement](https://raw.github.com/coronadoland/spring-js/master/LICENSE.txt)


### The last thing to know
Please enjoy.
